{"_id":"JInhHh6idtWffssf","name":"Nikola’s Reindeer","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"yywN1H4DZTTt2TUw","name":"Nikola’s Reindeer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are reindeer mutated by Nikola’s magic, \nand we crave to sink our teeth into the flesh of living creatures.</p>","notes":"Nikola's Pledge - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 121.","positive":"We are reindeer mutated by Nikola’s magic, \nand we crave to sink our teeth into the flesh of living creatures.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557640587,"modifiedTime":1781557640587,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HvYyuPmTcRU0ezRU","name":"Gift - Carnivore","type":"gift","img":"icons/svg/aura.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>Nikola’s Reindeer have large, clumsy jaws \nthat they use to eat meat. Each Reindeer in the herd increases \nits OL by 1 when it attacks a marked target. A target is marked \nwhen it suffers 1 Wound from a Reindeer bite. Alternatively, \na Reindeer can use its action to inflict a Wound on itself and \ncover up to 3 targets within 20 feet with blood to mark them. A</p>","notes":"Nikola's Pledge - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 121.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557640587,"modifiedTime":1781557640587,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1B7kG1LY4t5iIsmR","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>- Minor NPC (2 Wounds)\nDescriptor: We are reindeer mutated by Nikola’s magic, \nand we crave to sink our teeth into the flesh of living creatures. \nGift - Carnivore: Nikola’s Reindeer have large, clumsy jaws \nthat they use to eat meat. Each Reindeer in the herd increases \nits OL by 1 when it attacks a marked target. A target is marked \nwhen it suffers 1 Wound from a Reindeer bite. Alternatively, \na Reindeer can use its action to inflict a Wound on itself and \ncover up to 3 targets within 20 feet with blood to mark them. A</p>","notes":"Nikola's Pledge - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 121.","owner":"Nikola’s Reindeer","source":"Nikola's Pledge","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557640587,"modifiedTime":1781557640587,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"scenarioActorSlug":"lost-stories-nikolas-pledge-nikola-s-reindeer-121","collection":"Lost Stories","adventureSlug":"nikolas-pledge","adventureTitle":"Nikola's Pledge","sourceFile":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf","page":121,"role":"Minor NPC"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Nikola's Pledge","origin":"Lost Stories","role":"Minor NPC","notes":"<p>- Minor NPC (2 Wounds)\nDescriptor: We are reindeer mutated by Nikola’s magic, \nand we crave to sink our teeth into the flesh of living creatures. \nGift - Carnivore: Nikola’s Reindeer have large, clumsy jaws \nthat they use to eat meat. Each Reindeer in the herd increases \nits OL by 1 when it attacks a marked target. A target is marked \nwhen it suffers 1 Wound from a Reindeer bite. Alternatively, \na Reindeer can use its action to inflict a Wound on itself and \ncover up to 3 targets within 20 feet with blood to mark them. A</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":0,"max":0},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":2},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":3,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""},"threat":{"rank":"Easy 3","impulse":"","oppositionLevel":3}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557640587,"modifiedTime":1781557640587,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Kstu4ZK2G8hXefaK","name":"Villagers","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"GCU9MhHp321WVbBR","name":"Villagers - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Villagers","source":"The King's Awakening","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are poor villagers who sell vegetables and \nlivestock.</p>","notes":"The King's Awakening - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 182.","positive":"We are poor villagers who sell vegetables and \nlivestock.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Villagers","source":"The King's Awakening","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557643740,"modifiedTime":1781557643740,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Kk4eUTyTVXnB6EpS","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Villagers","source":"The King's Awakening","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>- Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: We are poor villagers who sell vegetables and \nlivestock.\nAgenda: Travel between island settlements to conduct business.\nInformation: Upon encountering them, the Storyteller \nrolls 1 die to determine which settlement the Villagers are \nfrom. The table below lists the information they can give \nthe Hunters, and in parentheses, who can give the information because they are from a particular settlement.</p>","notes":"The King's Awakening - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 182.","owner":"Villagers","source":"The King's Awakening","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557643740,"modifiedTime":1781557643740,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"scenarioActorSlug":"lost-stories-the-kings-awakening-villagers-182","collection":"Lost Stories","adventureSlug":"the-kings-awakening","adventureTitle":"The King's Awakening","sourceFile":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf","page":182,"role":"Minor NPC"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"The King's Awakening","origin":"Lost Stories","role":"Minor NPC","notes":"<p>- Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: We are poor villagers who sell vegetables and \nlivestock.\nAgenda: Travel between island settlements to conduct business.\nInformation: Upon encountering them, the Storyteller \nrolls 1 die to determine which settlement the Villagers are \nfrom. The table below lists the information they can give \nthe Hunters, and in parentheses, who can give the information because they are from a particular settlement.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":0,"max":0},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":1},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":3,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""},"threat":{"rank":"Easy 3","impulse":"Travel between island settlements to conduct business.","oppositionLevel":3}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557643740,"modifiedTime":1781557643740,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KxJhc6UYj8AaI8CM","name":"The Monkeys","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"a7TQ6UWHDNS6te86","name":"The Monkeys - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Monkeys","source":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>We are agile and fast, and we move quickly \nthrough the trees to escape threats.</p>","notes":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 155.","positive":"We are agile and fast, and we move quickly \nthrough the trees to escape threats.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Monkeys","source":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557642301,"modifiedTime":1781557642301,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"9Sjd1Q8qX1EWs86O","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Monkeys","source":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>- Minor NPC (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: We are agile and fast, and we move quickly \nthrough the trees to escape threats. \nAgenda: Satisfy the Giant’s hunger to prevent it from devouring us. \nThe Elephant-Eared Giant</p>","notes":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights - bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 155.","owner":"The Monkeys","source":"Journey of a Thousand and One Nights","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557642301,"modifiedTime":1781557642301,"lastMod